<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.1">
<l>teḷḷiyīr tēvarkkum tēvar tiruttakkīr</l>
<l>veḷḷiyīr veyya viḻuniti vaṇṇarō</l>
<l>tuḷḷunīrk kaṇṇa puramtoḻu tāḷivaḷ</l>
<l>kaḷviyō kaivaḷai koḷvatu takkatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wise one, god of gods, you who is suited to Tiru,</l>
<l>Pure one, oh, one the color of superior heated gold,</l>
<l>She worships [you] in Kaṇṇapuram with surging waters;</l>
<l>Is she a fraud? Is snatching her wrist bangles fitting?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
